    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly museum-quality vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been meticulously garage-kept and professionally detailed, the exterior is absolutely flawless with zero chips, dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear, the dashboard is crack-free, and every single electronic component\u2014from the climate control to the infotainment system\u2014functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete, documented service history from day one. The engine bay is pristine, and the car sits on a fresh set of high-performance tires with matching original alloy wheels. This vehicle has been treated with the utmost care, never seeing rain or snow, and comes complete with all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and detailed service records. It is, quite simply, the finest example of this model currently on the market, suited for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
